column5: Hey Pete, I hear that they are putting a Walmart at Fairview and Appleby!
I think the cure for cabin fever is just around the corner ... if not already here.  Everyone's too dang busy getting ready for openers.  Mods won't have much to do if we keep this up.

Well, we've hand plenty of diehard fans of a certain sports franchise, which shall remain unnamed, manifesting all the symptoms of an acute cabin fever.  Wait, that wasn't cabin fever; it's closer to a heart condition, like a broken heart.
Thats all we need eh Squid 2 Wall Marts within 2 blocks.Dan
Yeah musta been tough for the Habs fans to swallow .... getting blocked at the one yard line like that
What is going on with this site?? No one has had a meltdown yet!! No cabin fever, everyone is being civil. Sheesh!!
You're just getting mellow and more relaxed with your age, did you notice the change since your recent birthday?  Tony
Thats cause there is no ICE fishing, NO open Water fishing.. No new regs to&*%*&*(^&.. We need a a good flame going..  *just no personal attacks please*  Keeps it exciting..

For some of us who remember 99% of that " Older Than Dirt" thread, melting down just accelerates the inevitable. With the " golden years", yah, right, we come to realize that with all that we've survived, remembering the ones that we knew who didn't make it this far, life is far too short and you should carefully pick the issues that are worth blowing a gasket over.
Nah, it's not that life is short, it's the longest thing you're going to do but dang, you're a long time dead after.  Enjoy while you can.
LOL Squid, just because your a grumpy old man doesn`t mean we have to be!
My valium prescription hasn't run out yet Bud !
I'd be alot more upset, if I wasn't so heavily sedated! HH
Ouch  Good one Pete, I'm sure someone could stir the pot if you'd like  Whopper
what you need is a Krispy Kreme specialist....
OK, I'll start it off....  You're all idiots, your breath stinks, your opinion on politics is wrong because I said so and I will disagree with any hot button issue you support...  bring it.
Holy bejeezzzzzzz...... SHHHHHHHHHHH!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Squid just wait, the OOS bass picks should start to fire things up soon.
5 bucks says someone posts bass pics from up north that ARE in season and some people will assume that since they are closed in their area, they must be closed everywhere...
I could post some nasty comments about men and so forth.....maybe finish off with a few female issues..oh and throw in a few OOS Musky shots?  Would that help?  lol  bly

I think secretly T.J. and the moderators put in an "Instigator Penalty" rule just like the N.H.L. We are all now a "kinder and gentler" crowd highlighting our speed and skills. I draw the line at group hugs tho....  Hookset.
